Helm Charts

1. for various applications like Databases elk etc

2. templating enginge for yaml file = like microservice with different api versions or docker versions in yamls

Templates.yml with place holders and values.yaml   .values.name object with properties like container engine , container image, container ports

3. in CI/CD using Application Template file for pipeline and replace the values on the fly 

4. Application Helm Chart to be used in the Dev, Staging , Prod Application clusters

5. Release Management = Helm 2 has helm client and tiller 

Tiller = holds all histroy of the applied charts and versiosns of the charts applied
